Prager 20130920  03 Open Lines

 Issues raised include:

 how does Dennis demonstrate his love for his wife;

Prager 20130920  02 Happiness Hour: Unhappy Families of Genesis



Prager H2: People often think their family problems are unique,
 but the stories of Genesis suggest otherwise.


Prager 20130920  01 Dissonant Nurses

Prager H1: Nurses at a national conference greeted HHS Secretary Kathleen Sebelius
 with wild applause,
 cheering the arrival of ObamaCare.
 Then, in the question and answer period,
 the nurses told the Secretary why ObamaCare is going to be a nightmare.

 This is called cognitive dissonance
